Early Access Review

this game can be one the good ones, just need more work..you have todo the  tutorial to get some kind of idea ,in game map would be nice and the hacking what are those other files -cd rfid + ls+look to see if you see a SetMaster.exe then type that in and you have the unit....but what are the other files??..its alot of running, walking i mean alot it would be more than ok if you got better loot the Harvester gets stuck at times...npc can still go through walls..lol...the super jump takes to long at times,have to hold space bar for awhile just toget 8%...need more computer motherboards(aka LOOT ) for turrets ....toget more POWER seems tobe the thing todo..but for the most part for agame in alph an still new its not Bad..1 out 10 i give it 6 still work need tobe done-DO NOT BUY IF YOU DO NOT UNDERSTAND THAT....

for anyone wanting todo multiplyer snd me amessage or if you just want to explore.. :)

